<p>Texas Children&#39;s Design System provides a standardized, brand-compliant color palette. It uses a semantic naming system and numbered grading to help in the selection of colors that are thematically <strong>consistent</strong>, contextually <strong>meaningful</strong>, and <strong>accessible</strong> to those with low color perception.</p>

